		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1>The Visual Note Taking App That Organise Your Thoughts 
</h1>		
		<p>Picture Notes is the visual note taking app that help you to organise your images, video, recording and files to easily locate them later.</p>		
			<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.organize.data" role="button">
						Download Via Google play Store
					</a>
															<img width="1210" height="1141" src="https://picturenotes.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/save-1.png" alt="" loading="lazy" />															
			<h2>Connects with a wide variety of third-party apps. Integrate your chat with them to provide even</h2>		
				0
