			<h6>Features</h6>		
			<h2>Data management </h2>		
			<h5>01</h5>		
			<h5>Search Any Notes  </h5>		
		<p>Locate important notes containing your media files using keywords and phrases. “No more scrolling through your images endlessly to find that (one photo you can never seem to find)."</p>		
			<h5>02</h5>		
			<h5>Group All media Types In One Note</h5>		
		<p>Create personalised folders and link all your media content in one place. “Why not document the event how you’ll best remember it?”    </p>		
			<h5>03</h5>		
			<h5>Set up Reminders </h5>		
		<p>Set up and get reminders for essential notes. "Never forget about your big ideas!"</p>		
			<h6>making the perfect Picture Note
</h6>		
			<h2>How to make a note with the visual note taking app </h2>		
			<figure><img width="200" height="200" src="https://picturenotes.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/IDA.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></figure>Notes About Your BIG Idea <p>So, You got a great idea. Let’s add it to Picture Notes. You have a sketch, take a picture, hit upload. You have a crazy video Showing how it would work, upload that too... and you've got a voice recording of you doing an elevator pitch… add that. OK Let's put it all together, in one place, in Picture Notes - the visual note taking app 
</p>		
			<figure><img width="200" height="200" src="https://picturenotes.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/find.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></figure>Organise Your Thoughts to Remember More<p>Your mind is racing, so many amazing ideas and lots to learn, with lots to remember. Don’t worry. You can hit search and find “great idea #14”, which you saved 3 months ago. You can’t forget that one again, so why not set up a reminder to be alerted in 2 days.
</p>		
			<figure><img width="200" height="200" src="https://picturenotes.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/ORGANIS.png" alt="" loading="lazy" /></figure>Organise every occasion the way you remember it<p>Don't forget, you can create your own folders to group your ideas and events. You can also filter notes by the media they contain, as well as save extra special notes to your favourites. 
</p>		
			<h6>Pricing Plans</h6>		
			<h2>What's our monthly pricing subscription</h2>		
