			<figure><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.organize.data"><img width="1487" height="1439" src="https://picturenotes.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/recipe.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h4><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.organize.data">save recipes with images & videos </a></h4><p>Save and organize all your recipes in one place with Picture Notes complete with photos and videos
</p>		
			<figure><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.organize.data"><img src="https://picturenotes.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/Travel-scaled-q0advdxanxrh5nvm8slxwv75eeog67glbt95u9ig80.jpg" title="Travel" alt="Travel" /></a></figure><h4><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.organize.data">add Travel Notes files &amp; images </a></h4><p>Organize all your holiday memories and plans - from photos and videos to itineraries and notes.</p>		
			<figure><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.organize.data"><img width="2560" height="2489" src="https://picturenotes.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/cocktails-scaled.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy" /></a></figure><h4><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.organize.data">Create a bucket list</a></h4><p>Keep track of all the drinks you want to try with. From cocktails to craft beers, our app makes it easy to save notes, photos, and videos of the drinks you're most excited to taste</p>		
																<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.organize.data">
							<img width="194" height="58" src="https://picturenotes.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/google-play-black.png" alt="" loading="lazy" />								</a>
			<h2>Get Organized
</h2>		
		<p>Streamline your media management with Picture Notes the all-in-one app for uploading, organizing, and grouping all your photos and videos in one place, with features like search, filter, share, edit, favourites, and reminders to make it easy to keep track of your memories.</p>		
			<h3>Why Picture Notes</h3>		
			<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://picturenotes.co.uk/wp-content/plugins/elementor/assets/css/widget-icon-box.min.css">		
				<h4>
						Filter notes					
				</h4>
									<p>
						Filter notes by category and media type: This feature enables users to filter their notes by category or media type, making it easier to find specific types of media.					</p>
				<h4>
						 Keywords & phrase Search					
				</h4>
									<p>
						Search all notes with keywords and phrases: This feature allows users to search for specific notes using keywords and phrases, making it easier to find the notes they're looking for.					</p>
				<h4>
						Reminders & notifications					
				</h4>
									<p>
						Set up note reminders and notifications: This feature allows users to set reminders for their notes and receive notifications when the reminders are due, helping them stay on top of their notes and tasks.
					</p>
				<h4>
						Create favorites					
				</h4>
									<p>
						Add to favorites: This feature enables users to mark their favorite notes, making it easier to access the notes they use most often.					</p>
			<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.organize.data" role="button">
