		<title><![CDATA[privacy policy - FODMAP Checker]]></title>
		<link>https://picturenotes.co.uk/privacy-policy-privacy-policy-fodmap-checker/</link>
		<pubDate>Wed, 10 Jul 2024 19:15:31 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Lamar from Picture Potes]]></dc:creator>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">https://picturenotes.co.uk/?page_id=728</guid>
		<description></description>
		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>Privacy Policy for IBS FODMAP Checker</strong></p>
<p><strong>Effective Date: 10.07.2024</strong></p>
<p><strong>1. Introduction</strong></p>
<p>Welcome to IBS FODMAP Checker. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our application.</p>
<p><strong>2. Information We Collect</strong></p>
<p>We do not collect any personal data from users. The application requires access to your device's camera to take pictures of ingredient lists and access to your gallery to select photos for analysis.</p>
<p><strong>3. How We Use Your Data</strong></p>
<p>The images of ingredient lists taken or selected by users are sent to Google for text extraction. The extracted text is then sent to partners like OpenAI for analysis to determine if the ingredients are low FODMAP.</p>
<p><strong>4. Data Sharing</strong></p>
<p>We share data with the following third parties:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Google</strong>: For text extraction from images.</li>
<li><strong>OpenAI</strong>: For analyzing the extracted text to provide feedback on FODMAP content.</li>
</ul>
<p>Other than these uses, we do not share your data with any other third parties.</p>
<p><strong>5. Data Storage and Retention</strong></p>
<p>The images sent to Google are not stored on any cloud platform for future access. They are used solely for text extraction and are disregarded afterward. The text data sent to OpenAI is also used only for the purpose of analysis and is not stored by us.</p>
<p><strong>6. User Rights</strong></p>
<p>Since we do not store any personal data or identifiable information, there is no data tied to specific user accounts. Consequently, there is no data to access, correct, or delete upon user request.</p>
<p><strong>7. Data Security</strong></p>
<p>We partner with companies such as Google and OpenAI, which have robust security platforms and services. We ensure that data is anonymized and not tied to any user identity.</p>
<p><strong>8. Contact Us</strong></p>
<p>If you have any questions about our privacy practices, please contact us at: <a rel="noreferrer">feedback@picturenotes.co.uk</a>.</p>
<p><strong>9. Changes to This Privacy Policy</strong></p>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.</p>
<p><strong>10. Consent</strong></p>
<p>By using our application, you hereby consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.</p>]]></content:encoded>
