		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1>Account Deletion</h1>		
			<h2>Request Account Deletion</h2>		
		<p><strong>We respect your privacy and are committed to helping you manage your personal data. If you would like to request the deletion of your account and all associated data, please complete the form below.</strong></p>
<p><strong>Steps to Request Account Deletion:</strong></p>
<ol>
<li>Fill out the form below with the required information.</li>
<li>Once your request is submitted, we will process the deletion of your account and associated data within 30 days.</li>
<li>You will receive a confirmation email once your account has been deleted.</li>
</ol>
<p><strong>Data Deletion Policy:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Upon request, we will delete your account and all associated data from our systems.</li>
<li>Some data may be retained for legal or regulatory reasons and will be securely archived for the required period before being permanently deleted.</li>
<li>Data that will be deleted includes your profile information, any saved preferences, and usage history.</li>
</ul><br><p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team at:</p>		
					<ul>
							<li>
										Feedback@picturenotes.co.uk
									</li>
						</ul>
			<h2>Picture Notes is available for all android device</h2>		
		<p>Picture Notes is free to download and use via Google Play Store for the first 5 notes you upload</p>		
																<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.organize.data">
							<img width="194" height="58" src="https://picturenotes.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/google-play-black.png" alt="" loading="lazy" />								</a>
