ta-end=\"1008\">You must be at least <strong data-start=\"784\" data-end=\"800\">13 years old<\/strong> (or the age of digital consent in your country) to use Picture Notes. If you are under 18, you may only use the Service with permission from a parent or legal guardian who accepts these Terms on your behalf.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"1010\" data-end=\"1031\">3. Your Account<\/h2>\n<ul data-start=\"1032\" data-end=\"1206\">\n<li data-start=\"1032\" data-end=\"1132\">\n<p data-start=\"1034\" data-end=\"1132\">You are responsible for all activity on your account and the security of your login credentials.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1133\" data-end=\"1206\">\n<p data-start=\"1135\" data-end=\"1206\">Notify us immediately if you believe your account has been compromised.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 data-start=\"1208\" data-end=\"1229\">4. Your Content<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1230\" data-end=\"1326\">\u201cContent\u201d means photos, images, annotations, comments, or other material you upload or create.<\/p>\n<ul data-start=\"1327\" data-end=\"1656\">\n<li data-start=\"1327\" data-end=\"1383\">\n<p data-start=\"1329\" data-end=\"1383\"><strong data-start=\"1329\" data-end=\"1343\">Ownership.<\/strong> You keep all rights in your Content.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1384\" data-end=\"1556\">\n<p data-start=\"1386\" data-end=\"1556\"><strong data-start=\"1386\" data-end=\"1404\">License to us.<\/strong> You grant us a worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free license to store, display, and process your Content solely to operate and improve the Service.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1557\" data-end=\"1656\">\n<p data-start=\"1559\" data-end=\"1656\"><strong data-start=\"1559\" data-end=\"1571\">Privacy.<\/strong> Our handling of personal data is described in the <strong data-start=\"1623\" data-end=\"1655\">Picture Notes Privacy Policy<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 data-start=\"1658\" data-end=\"1685\">5. Prohibited Conduct<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"1686\" data-end=\"1709\">You agree <strong data-start=\"1696\" data-end=\"1703\">not<\/strong> to:<\/p>\n<ol data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"2175\">\n<li data-start=\"1710\" data-end=\"1816\">\n<p data-start=\"1713\" data-end=\"1816\">Upload Content that is illegal, hateful, harassing, sexually explicit, or infringes another\u2019s rights.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1817\" data-end=\"1891\">\n<p data-start=\"1820\" data-end=\"1891\">Use Picture Notes to stalk, harass, or violate the privacy of others.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"1892\" data-end=\"1999\">\n<p data-start=\"1895\" data-end=\"1999\">Reverse-engineer, decompile, or attempt to gain unauthorised access to the Service or its users\u2019 data.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2000\" data-end=\"2098\">\n<p data-start=\"2003\" data-end=\"2098\">Use automated means (bots, scrapers) to access the Service without our prior written consent.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2099\" data-end=\"2175\">\n<p data-start=\"2102\" data-end=\"2175\">Interfere with, disrupt, or degrade the Service or its security measures.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p data-start=\"2177\" data-end=\"2255\">We may remove Content or suspend accounts that violate these rules or the law.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"2257\" data-end=\"2318\">6. Subscriptions &amp; Payments&nbsp;<\/h2>\n<ul data-start=\"2319\" data-end=\"2653\">\n<li data-start=\"2319\" data-end=\"2445\">\n<p data-start=\"2321\" data-end=\"2445\">Certain features of Picture Notes require a <strong data-start=\"2365\" data-end=\"2399\">Pro \/ Premium subscription<\/strong> billed on a <strong data-start=\"2412\" data-end=\"2436\">monthly <\/strong>basis.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2446\" data-end=\"2542\">\n<p data-start=\"2448\" data-end=\"2542\">All fees are displayed in <strong data-start=\"2474\" data-end=\"2490\">GBP<\/strong>&nbsp;and are non-refundable except as required by law.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li data-start=\"2543\" data-end=\"2653\">\n<p data-start=\"2545\" data-end=\"2653\">You may cancel at any time; access to paid features continues until the end of the current billing period.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p data-start=\"2655\" data-end=\"2753\">Payments are processed by our partner <strong data-start=\"2693\" data-end=\"2725\">&nbsp;Paddle <\/strong>and subject to their terms.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"2755\" data-end=\"2793\">7. Intellectual-Property Notices<\/h2>\n<ul data-start=\"2794\" data-end=\"2985\">\n<li data-start=\"2794\" data-end=\"2880\">\n<p data-start=\"2796\" data-end=\"2880\"><span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">All software, design, and content we provide (excluding your Content) is owned by us or our licensors.<\/span><\/p><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 data-start=\"2987\" data-end=\"3016\">8. Third-Party Services<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"3017\" data-end=\"3195\">Picture Notes may link to or integrate with services provided by third parties (e.g., cloud storage or AI transcriptions). We are not responsible for their content or practices.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"3197\" data-end=\"3217\">9. Termination<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"3218\" data-end=\"3428\">You may delete your account at any time in the app settings.<br data-start=\"3278\" data-end=\"3281\">We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that breach these Terms, pose security risks, or create legal exposure for us or other users.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"3430\" data-end=\"3464\">10. Disclaimer of Warranties<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"3465\" data-end=\"3654\">The Service is provided <strong data-start=\"3489\" data-end=\"3520\">\u201cas is\u201d and \u201cas available.\u201d<\/strong> We do not guarantee that Picture Notes will be uninterrupted, secure, or error-free, or that Content will be preserved without loss.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"3656\" data-end=\"3689\">11. Limitation of Liability<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"3690\" data-end=\"3874\">To the maximum extent permitted by law, we will not be liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages, loss of data, or loss of profits arising from your use of the Service.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"3876\" data-end=\"3895\">12. Indemnity<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"3896\" data-end=\"4026\">You agree to defend and indemnify us against claims, damages, or expenses arising from your Content or your breach of these Terms.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"4028\" data-end=\"4062\">13. Governing Law &amp; Disputes<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"4063\" data-end=\"4312\">These Terms are governed by the laws of <strong data-start=\"4103\" data-end=\"4123\">{{jurisdiction}}<\/strong> without regard to conflict-of-law principles. Any dispute arising out of the Service will be resolved exclusively in the courts of <strong data-start=\"4256\" data-end=\"4269\">{{venue}}<\/strong>, unless applicable law requires otherwise.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"4314\" data-end=\"4346\">14. Changes to These Terms<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"4347\" data-end=\"4609\">We may update these Terms from time to time. If we make material changes, we will notify you via the app or email at least <strong data-start=\"4471\" data-end=\"4486\">{{30}} days<\/strong> before they take effect. Your continued use of Picture Notes after that date constitutes acceptance of the revised Terms.<\/p>\n<h2 data-start=\"4611\" data-end=\"4628\">15. Contact<\/h2>\n<p data-start=\"4629\" data-end=\"4686\">Questions? Reach us at <strong>feedback<a rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"4657\" data-end=\"4681\">@picturenotes.com.<\/a><\/strong><\/p>"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false}]]]></wp:meta_value>
